日工sick leave又好咩都好啦。。。。唉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}